若前揭基礎不存在，實難以建立長期之司法互助機制。<br />\n<br />\n本部呼籲香港政府除處理逃犯移交事宜外，更應重視與臺灣簽訂司法互助協議，建立臺港兩地共同打擊犯罪機制，以免臺港兩地成為在對方轄內犯罪者逃避法律制裁的避風港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.moj.gov.tw/cp-21-117152-73809-001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moj.gov.tw%2Fcp-21-117152-73809-001.html&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=022601c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.moj.gov.tw/cp-21-117152-73809-001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2bb8318a007579940e401c88ec396e5b352c0936","tid":1227843,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:14:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正氣！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c6166609853e07cf0f500b77a0179d308c6d2ddb","tid":1227843,"uid":19278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"371389d00f961a6c7c3cb577b6d0fdd9338ae790","tid":1227843,"uid":93236,"like":126,"dislike":0,"score":126,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"English連人地個下台階都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d397783de16210f8242ba2ed1c042b7354c74f2","tid":1227843,"uid":11448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b4faaac5d1101358b975a8f6f67b5925d204af7","tid":1227843,"uid":73856,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:50:29.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母俾人踢爆埋根本懶理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"第一日開始7婆就唔會理。中華民國嘅文件，邊個敢簽。"},{"pid":"089cc0d7189006e7e88b68123a49abd8b0c65650","tid":1227843,"uid":151933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"林鄭幫English刷民望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa